China’s Economy May Slow Significantly, Conference Board’s Van Ark Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-08-15T23:56:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-15/china-s-economy-may-slow-significantly-conference-board-s-van-ark-says.html
China’s economy  may slow quite
significantly over the next couple of months, Bart van Ark, the
chief economist of The Conference Board said today.  Van Ark spoke from  New York  in an interview with Bloomberg
Television ahead of the release of the New York-based research 
organization's leading economic indicator for the Chinese 
economy.  To contact the reporter on this story:
